===Phrase===
{{head|en|phrase|head=[[who]] [[know]]s?}}

# {{n-g|A [[rhetorical question]] asked to show that the person asking it neither knows the answer nor knows who might.}}
#: ''It could be one or the other, or both. '''Who knows?'''''
#: ''Do you think I'll get married before I turn 30?'' â€“ '''''Who knows''', you might never marry.''
# {{n-g|A rhetorical question asked to express the idea that anything is possible or that anything could happen.}}
#: {{ux|en|'''Who knows?''' Maybe someday he'll finish writing his book and make lots of money selling it.}}
#: {{ux|en|Since she hasn't studied at all I don't think she'll pass the test, but '''who knows'''?}}
#: {{ux|en|Don't touch that â€“ '''who knows''' where it's been?}}

